	(text "MCU PIN ASSIGNMENT / INTERFACE SUMMARY\n\nFunction        MCU Pin      Net Name        Direction / Notes\n---------------------------------------------------------------\nSWDIO           PA13         SWDIO           STDC14 debug / programming\nSWCLK           PA14         SWCLK           STDC14 debug / programming\nNRST            PF2          NRST            Hardware reset; connected to reset button and STDC14 RST\n\nBQ UART TX      PB6          UART1_TX        MCU TX -> BQ79600 RXD\nBQ UART RX      PB7          UART1_RX        BQ79600 TXD -> MCU RX\nBQ FAULT        PB4          BQ_FAULT_N      Active-low fault input from BQ79600\n\nI2C SDA         PB9          I2C_SDA         Shunt board / auxiliary I2C data\nI2C SCL         PB8          I2C_SCL         Shunt board / auxiliary I2C clock\nSHUNT ALERT     PB5          ALERT_SHUNT     Isolated alert input from shunt board\n\nCAN RX          PD0          CAN_RX          MCU receives from CAN transceiver RXD\nCAN TX          PD1          CAN_TX          MCU transmits to CAN transceiver TXD\nCAN STBY        PD2          CAN_STBY        CAN transceiver standby control\n\nGPIO Spare 1    PC1          GPIO_SPARE1     Reserved GPIO test / future expansion\nGPIO Spare 2    PC2          GPIO_SPARE2     Reserved GPIO test / future expansion\nGPIO Spare 3    PC3          GPIO_SPARE3     Reserved GPIO test / future expansion\nShutdown        PC0          SHUTDOWN        Shutdown output signal for system control\n\n3.3V Supply     VDD/VDDA     +3V3            MCU digital / analog supply\nGround          VSS/VSSA     GND             MCU ground / analog reference"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 246.126 123.444 0)
		(effects
